  <task><p>Compute the charge per mile in each city. (Do not include the initial charge.) In which city do taxis charge the highest mileage rate?</p></task>

            <commentary audience="instructor"><title>Note</title>
            <p>To help students with part (a), ask: if 1/8 mile costs $0.30, how much would 1 mile cost? You can also point out that dividing $0.30 by 1/8 mile gives the same result as multiplying $0.30 by 8.</p></commentary>

  <task><p>Write a linear model for the taxi fare in each city, using miles as the input variable. (Hint: What is the initial value for each model?)</p></task>
            <commentary audience="instructor"><title>Note</title>
